{"tid":2425291,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"4歲小蝗女[刷首]抽跌入水泥攪拌機，全身骨頭被攪碎！","createTime":"2021-02-27T08:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T15:20:56.000Z","uid":46678,"like":71,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"9322eb4271b5def0026279fc9a42cde54a7c4882","tid":2425291,"uid":46678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:58:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210227/VNJQ3JWO4NBSVNZGFT2GZMIB7Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210227%2FVNJQ3JWO4NBSVNZGFT2GZMIB7Q%2F&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm%2BDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=5ab33fb9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210227%2FVNJQ3JWO4NBSVNZGFT2GZMIB7Q%2F&h=5dfd6bf1\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210227/VNJQ3JWO4NBSVNZGFT2GZMIB7Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n中國湖南衡陽市祁東縣一名4歲女童， 誤闖工地後跌入水泥攪拌機，全身多處骨頭被攪碎，目前人昏迷在加護病房搶救。女童<span class=\"red\">父親怒批工地安全設施不足</span>，既沒圍擋，也無人值守，且兩台攪拌機都未斷電，當地警方已介入調查。<br />\n<br />\n工地負責人事後聯繫父親，提出賠償<span class=\"red\">3000元</span>（約1.3萬元台幣），後又加到5000元，但均被家屬拒絕。在警方協調下，施工方同意先支付5萬元（約22萬元台幣）的醫療費，後續賠償則繼續協商。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZwmpOn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZwmpOn.png&h=bc8df0a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3FESwto.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3FESwto.png&h=1b715635&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7c68c434e012f6735692b827f17845216975822","tid":2425291,"uid":123264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:59:16.000Z","msg":"識玩"},{"pid":"dc914c8973e2443552cd62f64ecbf5346f9ef81d","tid":2425291,"uid":301989,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:59:49.000Z","msg":"點解條屍睇落仲咁完整咁"},{"pid":"657a51cf23c2022a6ae89a299972d32a9441fb50","tid":2425291,"uid":103325,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"repl